## Task

Assign each source to the essay sections where it is most relevant. Your goal is to **spread sources evenly** across sections so that every section has strong citation support and every source is used at least once.

Rules:
- Every source MUST appear in at least one section's assignment.
- Every section MUST have at least {{ min_per_section }} assigned sources.
- A source MAY appear in multiple sections if genuinely relevant to each.
- Introduction and conclusion sections typically need fewer sources than body sections — but still assign at least {{ min_per_section }} to each.
- Assign based on **content fit** — the source's topic must genuinely support the section's key points and content outline. Do not assign a source to a section where it has no relevance.

